Authentication :
Method#1: Non secure way
auth plain base64 generated code
MAIL FROM: <senderEmail>
RCPT TO: <reciever email>
DATA
FROM: <SenderMail>
TO: <recieverEmail>
Subject: Subject of the mail
mail body
regards
